The paper is about improving the performance of recommender systems using deep learning methods, specifically with the use of review text. This falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The paper also introduces a new model, TransNets, which extends the DeepCoNN model by introducing an additional latent layer representing the target user-target item pair. This involves machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) for text processing.
